# Movie Search

Tiny API to search for movies on TheMovieDB and see a toplist of most searched for movies

## Installation

Use [npm] or [yarn]

```bash
yarn install
```

## Usage

```bash
yarn start
```

## Tests

```bash
yarn test
yarn test --watch (for watching changed files)
```

```bash
POST to /search with e.g. {term:'matrix'}
# should return a list of matching movies

GET to /most_searched
# should return a top list of most searched terms
```

